metadata.name: Queen Aja
metadata.description: Queen Aja is the queen of dawn, she was never born, just like dawn! Dawn is ever existent, even during the darkest night, dawn awaits your realization to appear before you! If you believe it, a dark night transforms into dawn! At your darkest hour, remember Queen Aja, she's always there, waiting for you to get out of your busy mind, to calm your inner storms, to believe again, right then she'll brighten your world!
